a competitor; an adversary; an antagonist:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or one's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"equal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"match, in courage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generally,"},{"kind":"text","text":"one's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"equal, match,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fellow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n42638","headword_ar":"قَرْنٌ","root":"qrn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"One's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"equal in age;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lidapN","text_ar":"لِدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tirobN","text_ar":"تِرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": with fet-h when relating to age, and with kesr when relating to fighting and the like. (Har, pp. 572,64.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaronN","text_ar":"قَرْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaronN mina Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"قَرْنٌ مِنَ النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A generation of men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"people of one time"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, * S, Ez-Zejjájee, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"succeeding another"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaron","text_ar":"قَرْن"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among whom is a prophet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"class of learned men, whether its years be many or few."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ez-Zejjájee, Msb.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaronN","text_ar":"قَرْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part of the head"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a human being"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which in an animal is the place whence the horn grows:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or [more exactly the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"temporal ridge"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SudogN","text_ar":"صُدْغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") i. e.] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edge of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haAmap","text_ar":"هَامَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(which is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle and main part of the head"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the cranium"},{"kind":"text","text":"]),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the right"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the left."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, in his “ Khalk el-Insán. ”) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quruwnN","text_ar":"قُرُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the head: see a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xay~aTa","text_ar":"خَيَّطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quruwnN","text_ar":"قُرُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of horses: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajam~u","text_ar":"اَجَمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaronN","text_ar":"قَرْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a solid hoof: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jub~apN","text_ar":"جُبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaronN","text_ar":"قَرْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a desert, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most elevated part."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jHf","text_ar":"جحف"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaronu A^aEofara","text_ar":"قَرْنُ اَعْفَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A spear-head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEofaru","text_ar":"اَعْفَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaronN","text_ar":"قَرْنٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pod, like that of the locust tree:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quruwnN","text_ar":"قُرُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". Occurring often in the work of AHn on plants, and in the TA, &c. See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAfN","text_ar":"غَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaronN","text_ar":"قَرْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a she-camel, which is like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eafal","text_ar":"عَفَل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a woman;"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2988},{"kind":"text","text":"and which is cauterized with heated stones. (AA, TA, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Efl","text_ar":"عفل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaronN","text_ar":"قَرْنٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An issue of sweat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quruwnN","text_ar":"قُرُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see two ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"san~a","text_ar":"سَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","JK","Msb","S"]},{"entry_id":"n42639","headword_ar":"قَرَنٌ","root":"qrn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiraAnN","text_ar":"قِرَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cord of twisted bark which is bound upon the neck of each of the ploughing bulls"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and to the middle of which is then bound the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luw^map","text_ar":"لُومَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whole apparatus of the plough"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fad~aAnN","text_ar":"فَدَّانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  [The pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqoraAnN","text_ar":"اَقْرَانٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sons of one mother from different men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayonN","text_ar":"عَيْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaranN","text_ar":"قَرَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEobapN","text_ar":"جَعْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}